Blizzard Project SCRUM Report: Week 1

Team B-Triple-J
Joseph Townsend, John Moreno, Jonathan Wang, Brandon Donohue

Our app should work on any web browser that supports WebGL.

App Features
•	Basic Earth object created
•	Basic Izzy object created
•	Single basic Arklet object created
•	Camera position adjustable
•	Zoom enabled
•	Earth properly rotates
•	Izzy properly moves away from Earth while rotating around it
•	Arklet properly follows Izzy

All objectives from week 1 were met.
In week 2 we plan to add texture to the Earth, create meteorite cloud around Earth, and create Arklet cloud around Izzy. 
